  <brief_title>Association Study Between CYP1A2 Gene Polymorphisms and Metabolism of Theophylline</brief_title>
  <official_title>Association Study Between CYP1A2 Gene Polymorphisms and Metabolism of Theophylline in Han and Uygur Patients With COPD</official_title>
