  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to determine whether common CYP1A2 gene polymorphisms effect
      metabolism of theophylline in Han and Uygur Patients with chronic obstructive pulmonary
      disease patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
